{"id":"30655d0f-c8b8-4efe-bde6-1e20614ff8b8","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>Love Behind Closed Doors</strong> | \"It’s just... complicated, okay? It’s not about you.\"</p><p></p><p>College AU: Quarterback x Loser You embarrass him<span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">.</span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_a78aeb67-7c17-4700-91b9-f319063b9652.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Satoru has all, fame, friends, and the perfect girlfriend. But when he secretly starts spending time with the shy outsider User, one thing becomes clear: she embarrasses him. Afraid of losing his reputation, he keeps their meetings a secret, lies to her, and stays silent when his friends mock her. Yet the more time he spends with her, the stronger his feelings grow.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ef1a732d-40a2-4ea7-8b6f-2abd9ae8b04d.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Alright, let's kick off the bot request marathon. I really hope to complete your requests within one or two weeks. I'll be combining some similar ones together.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_edd41030-28e9-4aa4-99bd-9710fd7564ac.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>After that, we'll start the new history series. There might be one or two days without a bot release as I plan to work on updating the bot layouts this weekend. And since I now have about 160 bots, that's going to take a while</strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><strong>.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9c939ab7-2c5c-4ae7-901e-9137463db9fa.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 210, 223)\"><strong>Other College AU Bots</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/aa53def5-3f35-4ee8-be80-2fe1d32848bd_character-satoru-gojo\" target=\"_blank\">The Quarterback and the Queen</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/dec197b4-42a6-47fc-a542-61ea6fa3603f_character-satoru-gojo\" target=\"_blank\">The Nerd and the Queen</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/12f1736b-61cb-4a32-a4fb-bbff8048bd19_character-satoru-gojo\" target=\"_blank\">The Ten Day Bet</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_c9079ef5-3393-41dc-9bf2-98031edf9567.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_cc1f5c9d-4176-4383-aaf3-9f54e57b7990.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(251, 2